%Tutorial --------------------------  EDIT  ---------------------------
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD
+
%                     -----------------------------------
                      ×      Edit Macro  "EDMODE"       ×
                      -----------------------------------
+
%BOUNDS :+
   Use%BOUNDS+to set the left and right bounds and save set them in the
   profile. It provides an easier way to change the bounds instead of se
   them in the bounds line (=BNDS>).
   Either both bounds must be specified. The first one specified (left-c
   number) must be smaller than the second (right).

   More topic will be presented in the EDIT tutorial.
+
+Enter%&EPF+to exit the tutorial and return to the EDIT modes control pa
+Hit%ENTER+to go on to the next tutorial panel
)INIT
  &EPF = PFK(END)
  IF (&EPF = &Z)
    &EPF = 'END'
  &D = TRUNC(&EPF,2)
  &DT = .TRAIL
  &D = TRUNC(&DT,1)
  IF (&D = '0')
    &DT = .TRAIL
    &EPF = 'PF&DT'
)PROC
)END
